title: Match of the Day - FA Cup Highlights - 8th March 2015- hdtv x264
description:
SPORT: Match of the Day: FA Cup Highlights
On: BBC 1 HD    
Date: Sunday 8th March 2015 
Time: 22:30 to 23:05 

Mark Chapman introduces highlights of the FA Cup quarter-final between seven-time winners Liverpool and Blackburn Rovers, who have lifted the cup on six occasions. Rovers, then also a second tier side, won 1-0 at Anfield in the last FA Cup meeting between the sides 15 years ago. Nathan Blake scored the winner that day in a fourth-round encounter. Liverpool saw off top-flight rivals Crystal Palace in the last round, whilst Blackburn have already knocked out Premier League duo Swansea and Stoke en route to the last eight.
